---
title: Sticky Baked Hoisin Chicken Thighs with Basmati Rice, Roasted Broccoli and Red Onion
description: This Sticky Baked Hoisin Chicken Thighs is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
